.TH "TODOPRO RAMBLE CONFIG" "1" "2026-02-27" "1.0.0" "todopro ramble config Manual"
.SH NAME
todopro\-ramble\-config \- Show or update Ramble configuration.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B todopro ramble config
[OPTIONS]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Show or update Ramble configuration.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-stt\fP TEXT
Default STT provider
.TP
\fB\-\-llm\fP TEXT
Default LLM provider
.TP
\fB\-\-silence\-timeout\fP INTEGER
Silence timeout (seconds)
.TP
\fB\-\-default\-project\fP TEXT
Default project name/ID
.TP
\fB\-\-language\fP TEXT
Default language
.TP
\fB\-\-show\fP
Show current config
